          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photon flux integrated from the threshold to the",
                " end-point energy was obtained from the activities of",
                " the (g,n) reaction products of seven elements with",
                " threshold energy from 8.02 to 10.79 MeV (Au, As, Ir,",
                "  Mn, Sn).",
                "These foils were irradiated with Dy to determine the",
                " absolute flux assuming linear shape of the photon",
                " flux up to the end-point energy (14 MeV).",
                "It results to the",
                " - 1.47(+/-0.45)E+08 photons/cm2/sec for the energy",
                "   range from the 156Dy(g,n) threshold (9.44 MeV) to",
                "   14 MeV,",
                " - 1.82(+/-0.45)E+08 photons/cm2/sec for the energy",
                "   range from  the 158Dy(g,n) threshold (9.04 MeV) to",
                "   14 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
